casebody.data:
No. 105,

Orig.

Kansas v. Colorado.

Motion of the Special Master for award of interim fees and expenses granted, and the Special Master is awarded a total of $83,082.76 to be paid by Kansas, Colorado, and the United States pursuant to the allocation order filed by the Special Master on October 9, 1989. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 489 U. S. 1005.]
